display_long_description:
Play as a weird little creature called a Fricklet, setting off on a long, unpredictable road trip to find your missing Gampy. Inspired by the chaotic energy of "Road to Gramby's" on Roblox (huge credit to them!), this game throws you into a strange world full of surprises, silly physics, and plenty of laughs.

Hop in your beat-up car and hit the road—solo or with your Fricklet friends. The journey is full of strange creatures, odd characters, and hidden items that can help (or sometimes hurt) as you travel across bizarre landscapes. Along the way, you'll find useful parts, tools, and random junk to collect, trade, or mess around with.

Driving is at the heart of the adventure, but you’re not always guaranteed a smooth ride. Whether you're trying to stay on course or accidentally running over your friends in a wild chase, every moment is part of the chaos. You can choose to work together or fight each other—it’s up to you.

There are also small side trips off the main path, with unexpected encounters and little detours that keep things fresh and weird.

This isn’t a serious game—it’s a silly, physics-driven sandbox made for laughs, exploration, and doing the dumbest things with your friends. Become a Fricklet, hit the road, and see just how far you'll get on your journey to find Gampy.
